= SDL_SaveBMP =
Use this function to save a surface to a file.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_SaveBMP(SDL_Surface* surface,
                const char*  file)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''surface'''
|^a pointer to the [[SDL_Surface]] to save^
|-
|'''file'''
|^a pointer to the file to fill with the surface data^
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

